@model KRBAccounting.Web.ViewModels.Student.StudentSearchViewModel
@using (Html.BeginForm("StudentSearch", "Student", FormMethod.Post, new { @class = "form-horizontal form-custom", id = "student-Info-form" }))
{
    <div id="bcPopupSearch" class="popup">
        <div class="head">
            <div class="arrow">
            </div>
            <span class="isw-zoom"></span><span class="name">Student Search</span>
            <div class="clear">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="body search">
            <div class="lag">
                <span class="stack">
                    <label class="label-100">
                        Registration No.</label>
                    <span class="field">
                        @Html.TextBoxFor(x => x.SrRegNo)
                    </span></span>
            </div>
            <div class="lag">
                <span class="stack">
                    <label class="label-100">
                        Student Name</label>
                    <span class="field">
                        @Html.TextBoxFor(x => x.SrStudentName)
                    </span></span>
            </div>
            <div class="lag">
                <label class="label-100">
                    Class</label>
                <span class="field">
                    <select name="SrClassId" id="SrClassId" class="chzn-select">
                        @foreach (var item in Model.SrClassList.Where(x => x.ProgramId == 0))
                        {
                            <option value="@item.Id">@item.Description</option>
                        }
                        @foreach (var item in Model.ProgramMasters)
                        {
                            <optgroup label="@item.Description">
                                @foreach (var i in Model.SrClassList.Where(x => x.ProgramId == item.Id))
                                {
                                    <option value="@i.Id">@i.Description</option>
                                }
                            </optgroup>
                        }

                    </select>
                </span>
            </div>
            <div class="clear">
            </div>
            <div class="lag">
                <span class="stack">
                    <label class="label-100">
                        Roll No.
                    </label>
                    <span class="field">
                        @Html.TextBoxFor(x => x.SrRollNo, new { @class = "input-160 input", id = "student_type_search" })
                    </span></span>
            </div>
            <div class="clear">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <input type="submit" class="btn" value="Search" style="margin-left: 13px;" />
            <a class="btn btn-danger link_bcPopupSearch">Close</a>
        </div>
    </div>
}
<div class="clear">
</div>
